author: @omsaikommawar
text: 🎥 Machine learning and deep learning are still relevant in 2024 for generative AI and data science careers.   #### Highlights - 🏢 Many big companies like Meta, Google, and OpenAI are using generative AI and working towards creating AGI. - 💼 Job interviews in the data science industry focus on basic machine learning and deep learning algorithms. - 🌐 Companies solving generative AI use cases are using both open-source models and traditional ML/DL techniques. - 🔒 Data privacy and security are major limitations in using generative AI models. - 🎨 Generative AI models have limitations in creativity and following specific patterns. - 💰 Traditional ML/DL techniques have become more efficient, scalable, and cost-effective. - 🚀 Learning ML and DL techniques is still valuable for future career opportunities in generative AI.
